    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it doesn't feel like healing helps. it just feels like i'm performing for people. i just feel so disconnected from the living, you know? like he's over there in some peaceful place and i'm stuck here in this gray, loud, miserable world. i just wonder if there's any point in fighting to stay here when everything i loved is gone.",
